column5: It was a cold morning. Set up on one spot and stayed. A couple of quick fish by 9 or so, then gave my goby bug a try. Ya baby,it worked. Tom S, those hooks are so super sticky. Thanks again
nice going dude be verwy verwy quiet hehehehehe were hunting that wrackally  whitefish
"ON THE GOBY FLY!!!!"  could be heard all around the bay.
Lol. Good to see it working for you Brian.
Nice job Brian.  Very cool on your own fly!  Mark
